{"id":"jerahmeel","term":"Jerahmeel","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Loving God. (1.) The son of Hezron, the brother of Caleb (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 2:9\">1 Chr. 2:9</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 2:25\">25</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 2:26\">26</a>, etc.).</p>\n<p>(2.) The son of Kish, a Levite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 24:29\">1 Chr. 24:29</a>).</p>\n<p>(3.) Son of Hammelech (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Jeremiah 36:26\">Jer. 36:26</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 2:9","1 Chronicles 2:25","1 Chronicles 2:26","1 Chronicles 24:29","Jeremiah 36:26"]}